==English==

===Pronunciation===
*kărˈə-văn, /ˈkærəvæn/, /"k{r@v{n/

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[convoy]] or procession of travelers, their [[vehicle]]s and cargo, and any [[pack animal]]s, especially [[camel]]s crossing a [[desert]].
# {{cattag|UK|Australia}} a furnished vehicle [[tow]]ed behind a car etc and used as a dwelling when stationary.

